# CODEOWNERS
#
# This file defines code ownership for the Oz AI repository.
# Each pattern on the left matches a set of files. The GitHub usernames
# or team names on the right are required reviewers for PRs that modify
# matching files.
#
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Replace placeholder usernames with actual GitHub usernames before use.

# === Global Default ===
# All files require review from the engineering lead unless a more specific
# rule below applies.
*                               @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === Documentation ===
# All documentation changes require review from the technical writer or lead.
/docs/                          @oz-ai-engineering-lead
/design/                        @oz-ai-engineering-lead
README.md                       @oz-ai-engineering-lead
.cursor/rules.md                @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === Architecture-Critical Files ===
# These files define the project's architectural foundation.
# Changes require the engineering lead's explicit approval.
/docs/01_PROJECT_BRIEF.md       @oz-ai-engineering-lead
/docs/02_ARCHITECTURE.md        @oz-ai-engineering-lead
/docs/04_DECISIONS.md           @oz-ai-engineering-lead
docker-compose.yml              @oz-ai-engineering-lead
pyproject.toml                  @oz-ai-engineering-lead
package.json                    @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === Agent Layer ===
# All agent code and system prompts require lead review.
/agents/                        @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === Guardian Agent ===
# The Guardian Agent requires separate explicit review — changes here
# affect the entire platform's safety posture.
/agents/guardian/               @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === MCP Tool Layer ===
# MCP tools are the agent-to-system interface. Changes require review.
/mcp/                           @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === Backend ===
/backend/                       @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === Frontend ===
/frontend/                      @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === Evaluation ===
# Evaluation scenarios and harness define the quality bar.
/evaluation/                    @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === Security-Sensitive Files ===
.env.example                    @oz-ai-engineering-lead
/docker/                        @oz-ai-engineering-lead
/.github/SECURITY.md            @oz-ai-engineering-lead

# === GitHub Templates ===
/.github/                       @oz-ai-engineering-lead
